{{term|1=Wing }}
{{defn|no=1 |1= A lateral part or projection of a building or structure such as a [[wing wall]]. }}
{{defn|no=2 |1= A subordinate part of a building possibly not connected to the main building.<ref>"Wing" def. 9. a. ''Oxford English Dictionary'' Second Edition on CD-ROM (v. 4.0) © Oxford University Press 2009</ref> }}
{{defn|no=3 |1= The sides of a [[stage (theatre)]]. }}
{{glossary end}}

